# Screenshots Directory

Place your application screenshots here with the following naming convention:

- `projects-page.png` - Projects dashboard
- `kanban-board.png` - Kanban board with drag-and-drop
- `issue-detail.png` - Issue detail page
- `search-page.png` - Search with filters
- `notifications.png` - Notifications center
- `activity-feed.png` - Activity timeline
- `dark-mode.png` - Dark theme example
- `project-settings.png` - Project settings page

Recommended size: 1920x1080 or similar 16:9 aspect ratio
Format: PNG or JPG
